  call deoplete#custom#option('sources', {
        \ 'ruby': ['syntax', 'buffer', 'member', 'omni', 'LanguageClient', 'ultisnips', 'around'],
        \})
  autocmd CompleteDone * silent! pclose!

  " fzf key bindings
  nnoremap <Leader>f :<C-u>Files<CR>
  nnoremap <Leader>b :<C-u>Buffers<CR>
